articles.title: Ariana Grande, Cynthia Erivo and Jonathan Bailey Bid Farewell to Oz as ‘Wicked: For Good’ Cast Thrills London at Europe Premiere - The Hollywood Reporter
articles.description: In their last outing as Glinda, Elphaba and Fiyero, respectively, the trio lead Jon M. Chu's 'Wicked' follow-up, set for a Nov. 21 theatrical release.
articles.content:
Ariana Grande and Cynthia Erivo are officially saying goodbye to Glinda and Elphaba for good.
